descriptionHtml:
[center][u][b]Vilinija[/b][/u]
[size=2]female breton preset for slot #5, [/size]but it'll work on nords and imperials.
might need a bit of personal tweaking tho

[b][u]required mods:
[/u][/b][size=1](you need these for my preset to look the same)
[/size]
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12951/?]ECE[/url] (1.4)
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35713/?]ECE Enhancer
[/url]- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/57440/?]ECE More Body Sliders[/url]
(I'm using UNPCM body, so body might be slightly different
if you're using any other body mod)
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/73853/?]Pure Skin Texture[/url] (+ hi res tintmask option)
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]Eyes of Beauty[/url] (overwrite with [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/54416/?]Eye Normal Fix[/url] and [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/67447/?]Improved Cube Map[/url] - Less Reflection version)
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/?]SG Female Eyebrows[/url]
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS Hairdos[/url]

[u]recommended mods:
[/u][size=1](not required but they're pretty sweet)
[/size]
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35303/?]Female Facial Animation[/url] (+ optional mouth)
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49168/?]Eyebrow Specularity Fix[/url]
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/69584/?]UNP Tender Hands[/url]
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/71063/?]Facelight Plus[/url]

I don't care what you do with the preset as long as you don't claim it as your own
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/56812/?]UnkoENB[/url] is being used in the screenshots! thanks to my friend for taking some of the screenshots for me
thanks to all the modders for the mods used to make this preset[/center]
author: anaonns
